name: Come Play
description:
Come Play

It reminds me of "play"
I was transported to the past (children) where I often went to a friend's house or somewhere without knowing what to play there, even though there would be a friend who would bring a game tool and invite them to play together.

that's how I feel in this photo, I left with no plans to play with my camera. Then seen from afar someone was skateboarding, I came but I didn't go skateboarding, I played line and shadow.
